Variable Description: depression_and_anxiety: Measure of total depressive and anxiety disorder diagnoses from mental health professional. Pt gets 0 for no depressive or anxiety disorders, 1 for depressive and anxiety disorders, 2 for only depressive disorders, and 3 for only anxiety disorders. Depressive disorders include major depressive disorder, pre-menstrual depressive disorder and postnatal depressive disorder. Anxiety disorders include GAD, social anxiety/phobia, specific phobia, agoraphobia, panic attacks and panic disorder.

Variable Description: restricting_vs_binge_eating_eating_disorders: Measure of total eating disorders with restrictive eating against eating disorders with binge eating. Value: Pt gets 0 for no eating disorder diagnosis, 1 for anorexia nervosa or atypical anorexia nervosa and 2 for bulimia nervosa or binge eating disorder.
Value Description: Measure of total eating disorders with restrictive eating against eating disorders with binge eating. Diagnoses from mental health professional.

Variable Description: bipolar_and_schizophrenia: Measure of bipolar and psychosis disorder diagnoses from mental health professional. Pt gets a 0 for no psychotic or bipolar disorder, 1 for psychotic and bipolar disorder, 2 for psychotic disorder only and 3 for bipolar disorder only. Psychotic disorders include schizophrenia, schizoaffective and other psychotic disorder. Bipolar includes bipolar disorder, manic depression, mania or hypomania.

phq.sum_score_retro_raw: Reflects the pt's total pre-pandemic PHQ (depression) symptoms measured retrospectively during the COPING baseline, without pt's sum score being converted to NA if they don't answer all the symptom questions. Numeric scale from 0-27.
Value Description: No label. Raw score values of phq.scored_items_retro

Variable Description: phq.sum_score_base_raw: Reflects pt's total PHQ symptoms at the COPING baseline, without pt's sum score being converted to NA if they don't answer all the symptom questions. Numeric scale from 0-27.
na_per_person_phq_retro: Measure of the amount of NA's in the PHQ-9 items. Pt answered based on GAD symptoms during pandemic. About pre-pandemic symptoms. Numeric scale starting at 0
Value Description: Measure of the amount of NA's in the PHQ-9 items. Pt answered based on GAD symptoms during pandemic

Variable Description: phq.missing_only_suicide_item_retro: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's a person had before the pandemic was 1 and that phq.dead_hurting_thoughts_prepan_numeric is NA. Pre-pandemic symptoms. No (0), Yes (1).

phq.missing_only_suicide_item_retro: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's a person had before the pandemic was 1 and that phq.dead_hurting_thoughts_prepan_numeric is NA. Pre-pandemic symptoms. No (0), Yes (1).
na_per_person_phq_base: Measure of the amount of NA's in the PHQ-9 items. Pt answered based on GAD symptoms during pandemic.  COPING baseline (GLAD, EDGI, NBR). Numeric scale starting at 0
Value Description: Measure of the amount of NA's in the PHQ-9 items. Participant answered based on GAD symptoms during pandemic. COPING baseline (GLAD, EDGI, NBR).

Variable Description: phq.missing_only_suicide_item_base: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's a person had before the pandemic was 1 and that phq.dead_hurting_thoughts_prepan_numeric is NA. COPING baseline (GLAD+NBR+EDGI). No (0), Yes (1).

phq.missing_only_suicide_item_base: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's a person had before the pandemic was 1 and that phq.dead_hurting_thoughts_prepan_numeric is NA. COPING baseline (GLAD+NBR+EDGI). No (0), Yes (1).
phq.sum_score_base: Reflects participants total PHQ symptoms at the COPING baseline. Numeric scale from 0-27.
Value Description: Total PHQ symptom score at COPING baseline

Variable Description: phq.sum_score_8items_base: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's per person who filled out PHQ was greater than one and that phq.missing_only_suicide_item_prepan equaled 1. COPING baseline (GLAD+NBR+EDGI). Numeric score from 0 to 27
Value Description: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's per person who filled out PHQ was greater than one and that phq.missing_only_suicide_item_prepan equaled 1. COPING baseline (GLAD+NBR+EDGI).

Variable Description: phq.sum_score_retro: Measure of the pt's total pre-pandemic PHQ symptoms as measured retrospectively during the COPING baseline. About pre-pandemic symptoms. Numeric scale from 0-27. Created by summing the phq "_retro" symptom items. Responses include COPING GLAD, EDGI and NBR pt's.
Value Description: No label. Measure of the pt's total pre-pandemic PHQ symptoms as measured retrospectively during the COPING baseline

Variable Description: phq.sum_score_8items_retro: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's per person who filled out PHQ was greater than one and that phq.missing_only_suicide_item_prepan equaled 1. Pre-pandemic symptoms. Numeric score from 0 to 27
Value Description: Variable created on the conditions that the number of NA's per person who filled out PHQ was greater than one and that phq.missing_only_suicide_item_prepan equaled 1. Pre-pandemic symptoms

time_diff_coping_awareness_march_1: Variable created to look at the difference between start date for COPING (time1) minus the start date for GLAD(time2) (time1-time2). Numeric scoring up to 29.
Value Description: Variable created to look at the difference between start date for COPING (time1) minus the start date for GLAD(time2) (time1-time2).

Variable Description: time_diff_coping_first_case_uk_jan_31: Difference between first COVID-19 case in the UK to the COPING baseline. Numeric scoring up to 33.
Value Description: No label - reflects time diff between sign up to COPING and first COVID-19 case in UK

Variable Description: time_diff_signup_lockdown_march_23: Time difference between the first COVID lockdown on 23rd March to when the GLAD and EDGI pt's signed up to these studies. Numeric scoring up to 80.
Value Description: No label - reflects time diff between sign up to GLAD/EDGI and

Variable Description: time_diff_signup_awareness_march_1: Variable created to look at the difference between start date of the pandemic (time1) minus the start date for sign up questionnaire for EDGI or GLAD (time2) (time1-time2). Numeric scoring up to 77.
Value Description: Variable created to look at the difference between start date of the pandemic (time1) minus the start date for sign up questionnaire for EDGI or GLAD (time2) (time1-time2).

Variable Description: time_diff_signup_first_case_uk_jan_31: Time difference between first case of COVID-19 in the UK against when the GLAD and EDGI pt's joined these studies. Numeric scoring up to 72.
Value Description: No label - time difference between first case of COVID-19 in the UK and the pt's sign up to GLAD/EDGI

Variable Description: time_diff_sign_up_coping: Variable created to look at teh difference between the start date for COPING (time1) and the start date for GLAD (time2) (time1-time2). Numeric scoring up to 101.
Value Description: Variable created to look at the difference between the start date for COPING (time1) and the start date for GLAD (time2) (time1-time2).
